Text: AVG reports a trojan in the keygen...

Well I was able to generate valid keys by running the keygen in an isolated VM. Hopefully someone with more knowledge than me can get a clean version of the keygen from this and post it. Not really any need to include the installer as that can be downloaded from the developer's site.
Just your typical "hack tool" alert, no virus in the keygen.

Am i confused or.. this its Business Edition... and not Extreme Edition..

Anyway, i tried it on Extreme Edition which i downloaded from official site, the keygen doesnt work, any ideas?

Nice one thanks. "NO" viruses or trojans! Thats what you get if you use cheap rubbish anti-virus software like AVG, Fulse positives!!
